text: Ana Paula Vitorino (born 1962) is a Portuguese politician serving as Minister of Sea . She is a member of the Socialist Party. From 2005 to 2009, Vitorino served as the Secretary of State for Transport. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Government ministers of Portugal Category:Women government ministers of Portugal Category:Socialist Party (Portugal) politicians
